features: 【Easy, Ultra-Fast to Play】CL206 wired computer keyboard is super easy to use, it works instantly with any USB devices, no driver needed, no need to worry about interference that breaks your connection, no charging or battery consumption.

【Responsive Low-Profile Chiclet Keys】Provide optimized responsiveness and effortless tactile feedback that remind you the key has been hit. You can type with confidence with shorter keystroke travel so it’s decent to type on for long periods.

【Slim, Modern Design】Own your style with a slim computer keyboard with premium matte finish, and you can easily carry it when you work from home. This keyboard is compact and doesn't take up a lot of real estate on the desk, great if you have a small office workspace.

【Ergonomic, Noiseless Typing】The keyboard angle is adjustable with flip out legs, supporting your hands in a more ergonomic gesture to relieve fatigue and ensure comfortable typing experience. No need to worry about disturbing others around because it has 50%-reduced click noise.

【Optimize Your Productivity】Boost your workflow and simply how you use your computer with a large number pad, 3 indicator lights and 12 multimedia shortcuts, including video, volume, surfing, email control etc.

【Spill-Resistant, UV Letters】Keyboard has waterproof protection on its surface and drain holes design on the back, preventing damage by accidental spills and can be simply wiped dry. The characters on keycaps are extremely hard to wear thanks to the high quality UV coating.

【Compatibility, 18 Months Warranty】Work fluidly on Windows 7/8/10/11/XP/Vista/Server/Chrome OS/Mac OS/Linux/TV. Contact COLIKES for any instructions/replacement/refund. 【No need to return the old one.】

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Unexpectedly comfortable keyboard
reviews.reviewText: Getting used to a new keyboard is something that made me very apprehensive to make the switch, but the keys are very easy to reach and they respond well to my touch. No real "bells or whistles" on this, but it is very efficient and contains the essentials: function, windows, and 10-key all with the standard keyboard. The price was in a fair range and no difficulty installing and using right away. Design is lightweight, but it's sturdy and has "legs" if you prefer to slant the keyboard. The cord is a good 3 feet long.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Affordable price. Quality doesn’t disappoint. I had it for a few months and it is functioning to perfection. Will buy again when needed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Decent, but lights for CAP, etc., are dim... too dim
reviews.reviewText: A decent, cheap keyboard on sale. The keys are smooth enough, but the lights for NUM, CAP, etc. are tiny, dim and recessed to the point, you can't see them from a sitting position.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good keyboard so far
reviews.reviewText: As soon as I saw this keyboard, I knew I needed it. I love the colour yellow.I got it the same day of writing this review but I will update if I run into any issues... But about the keyboard !It's a keyboard. The colour is all that it really has going for it, although even that is less vibrant than I expected. It's very light-weight and the plastic has... texture to it. I am very sensitive when it comes to texture so it might be less noticeable to others but the plastic is not smooth, I can say that.It's going to take some getting used to but that's usual when switching keyboards. It's been good so far though ! No reason to not give five stars (yet but hopefully never).Keyboard :)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for my mother in law that works from home. The packaging was not over done. It was fairly easy to get out. It came out looking just like the pictures. It arrived quickly and she was able to set up by herself. She has a think pad (laptop). The connection is constant and very easy to set up. She is very happy with her new keyboard and prefers it over the laptop keyboard.
